org.net4care.forwarder

Interface Query

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    QueryPersonTimeInterval, QueryPersonTimeIntervalType, QueryWithBadQueryType

    public interface Query
    Any query for a set of observations must implement this interface. NOTE! Developers of client applications need not care about this interface, only the concrete classes in the 'query' subpackage are relevant as these are the only ones that can be handled by the server.
    Author:
    Net4Care, Henrik Baerbak Christensen, AU

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  Query.QueryResponseType
      Define the type of the returned observations from a query, either STO's or PHMR's.
